%% Diagram: 103 Early Hints overlap server think-time with browser preload
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant B as Browser
    participant E as CDN edge
    participant O as Origin
    participant S as Asset host

    Note over B,S: Without Early Hints — browser idles during origin think-time
    B->>E: GET /page (HTML)
    E->>O: forward
    Note right of O: ~300 ms render
    O-->>E: 200 OK + HTML
    E-->>B: 200 OK + HTML
    B->>S: GET /critical.css (after HTML parse)
    S-->>B: 200 OK

    Note over B,S: With 103 Early Hints — preload runs in parallel with render
    B->>E: GET /page (HTML)
    E-->>B: 103 + Link preload critical.css
    par Browser preloads
        B->>S: GET /critical.css
        S-->>B: 200 OK
    and Origin still rendering
        E->>O: forward
        O-->>E: 200 OK + HTML
        E-->>B: 200 OK + HTML
    end
